ISLAMABAD, Mar 10 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib Thursday said that Fazlur Rehman’s private militia invaded and tried to spread fear and panic by attacking Parliament Lodges.
In a Tweet, he said, it should be remembered that not only the members of the Assembly live in the Parliament Hostel but also their families.
